      "protocol": {
        "framing": "soundcore_v1",
        "_doc": "host->device: 08 ee 00 00 00 <cmd:2> <len:2 LE total> <payload..> <crc(sum8)>. device->host: 09 ff 00 00 01 <cmd:2> <len:2 LE> <payload..> <crc>. Command bytes = OpenSCQ30 Command([hi,lo]).",
